\id 3JN 3 JHN Lugulu Bible Version 
\h 3 Yohane 
\toc1 Ibaluwa ya Kadatu ya Yohane 
\toc2 3 Yohane 
\toc3 3 Yoh 
\mt2 Ibaluwa ya kadatu ya 
\mt1 Yohane 
\imt1 Ichilongole 
\ip Ibaluwa ya kadatu tsayandikighwa na mtumighwa Yohane mne miyaka ya tisini kulawa Yesu helekighwe, Yohane ng'alongile bae ka yeye iye iyandike, ila kekema imwenyegho mbala (3 Yohane 1:1). Kuya kotenda pfipfo mne (2 Yohane 1:1) Yotogholighwa ka Yohane hayang'ali yokala Efeso tsakandika Imbuli Inoghile, na tsibaluwa tsingi ndatu, Ibaluwa ya Mwanduso, ya Keli na aino ya Kadatu. 
\ip Yohane tsakamwandikila ibaluwa ino imunu we Imulungu iyakemighwe Gayo. Komkema Gayo sale yake, na komlaghitsa awatendele uluso Wakiristu wangi iwobita mna isi yawo. 
\iot Ighali mno 
\io1 Isula ya 1:1 Yohane koitambula ibaluwa yake. 
\io1 Isula ya 1:2-8 komghuma Gayo ghumoyo na komlaghitsa aghendelele na uluso. 
\io1 Isula ya 1:9-12 kolonga mbuli tsa iwanu wangi weli, Diyotelefe na Demetiliyo. 
\io1 Isua ya 1:13-14 komalitsila ibaluwa yake. 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Nene imbala nokwandikila ghweghwe Gayo, yanikunoghela mna ukweli. 
\p  
\v 2 Sale yangu, nokulombela pfinu pfako pfighende ghoya na uwe mghima, ka muhe wako pfaughendelela ghoya.  
\v 3 Tsandeng'elela ng'ani hanihulike ndughu wangi iwatsile hano na kunongela pfaukindilisa ukweli na pfaughendelela kukala mne ukweli.  
\v 4 Kuduhu ichinu ichinideng'elesa ng'ani kubita kuhulika ka wanangu wokala mne ukweli. 
\s1 Ukuwasang'anila wandughu 
\p  
\v 5 Sale yangu, ghweghwe kwa wakutogholighwa mne sang'ano tsuwasang'anila wandughu, ghendoghendo kwa wahenza.  
\v 6 Iwanu awo walilongela kanisa lya hano mbuli tse unoghelo wako. Kutsotenda ghoya ung'awapfila waghendelele ne ghumwanza ghwawo kwa inzila iimnoghela Imulungu.  
\v 7 Mana wakwandusa ghumwanza ghwawo mne ukumsang'anila Kiristu bila kubokela chinu kulawa kwe iwanu ing'awommanya Imulungu.  
\v 8 Twetwe Wakiristu twobamighwa kuwapfila iwanu ka wano, ili tusang'ane nawo kwaajili ye ukweli. 
\s1 Diyotelefe na Demetiliyo 
\p  
\v 9 Tsanilyandikila ibaluwa kanisa, lekeni Diyotelefe, iyobama yawe chilongotsi, kolema ghendo kutuhulikitsa.  
\v 10 Ning'atsa nitsogheka mwatsi ghose ghayatendile, aghala ghehile ghayatulongile na ghayotubangitsila! Kuya yeye kolemagha kuwabokela wandughu wayetu, pfipfila kowaghoma awala iwobama kuwabokela, na kowawinga kulawa mne kanisa. 
\p  
\v 11 Sale yangu, uleke kuwinza ghehile, ila ughawinze ghanoghile. Imunu wowose iyotenda ghanoghile kolawa kwe Imulungu. Na imunu wowose iyotenda ghehile ng'amwonile bae Imulungu. 
\p  
\v 12 Iwanu wose wolonga ghoya mbuli tsa Demetiriyo, na ukweli nawo wolonga pfipfo. Pfipfila twetwe wose twolonga pfinoghile mbuli tsake, naghwe kwomanya ka twolongesa. 
\s1 Ndamso tsa usighilo 
\p  
\v 13 Tsang'ala ne tsimbuli nyingi tsa kuwalongela, lekeni sibama bae kukwandikila.  
\v 14 Nololela kukwona sambi, kuya tutsolonga chihanga kwa chihanga. 
\p  
\v 15 Ukale tseghamba. 
\p Sale tsetu iwali hano wokulamsa. Kuya walamse sale tsetu wose iwali ako, chila munu.